I’m so happy this @kgbglass piece has come home! Story time!
.
I grew up near a @downinthevalley and use to go in with my parents all the time. Eventually when I was old enough I worked at said DITV. This was before “heady glass” took off and nobody knew what this gem really was. I knew. I was able to talk the manager at the time to sell it to me for $20 off the sticker price and it was mine for $100 cash. .
Later find out this is an early 2012 donut that was sold to a wholesale company. .
I traded this donut for a pendent a few years back when something I really wanted was on the market. Just last week I was this for sale on a Facebook group and was able to convince the guy to sell it back to me. I’m very thankful this donut is home!
